snippet.title: Aquaman, Jason Mamoa, Amber Heard, Nicole Kudman, Willem Dafoe
snippet.description:
Aquaman (2018), from birth to become king of Alantis, fell in love with Mera and bring peace to the land and the sea...
Aquaman by Jason Mamoa
Mera by Amber Heard
Atlanna by Nicole Kidman
Nuidis Vulko by Willem Dafoe
Directed by James Wan
Budget $160-200 million
Box Office so far (23 December 2018) $383.4 million
The background song is What the World Needs Now by Jackie DeShannon.
